@node CHGW "Changed sites list Window"

    @{FG shine}-< Changed sites list Window >-@{FG text}


  In this window GuardAmy will add all the sites that have the @{b}add in changed sites list@{ub}
 check mark selected. The 4 buttons below are used to remove selected items from the list
 or to clear this list, and to send the current item URL to browser (using OpenURL.library,
 see @{"settings" link CONFIG} section to know how to set this library) and to clipboard.

  Pressing the right mouse button on the list will open a context menu that contains the
 same functions of the buttons (except the @{b}Remove All@{ub} one).

  Note that closing the window will not clear this list and that sites are added dinamically
 while checking them also if the window is closed.

@endnode

@node CHANGES "History"

    @{FG shine}-< History >-@{FG text}


  @{b}ver. 1.2@{ub}  - first of all note that my email address is changed :) refere to
              the new one to contact me

            - in the installer script changed "YamExpansion" with "GuardAmy"...
